            "title": "Professional Experience",
            "summary": "Experienced compliance and risk manager with deep knowledge of global regulatory requirements and hands-on experience developing and implementing risk policies for a multinational publicly traded FinTech company. CAMS-certified AML/CTF specialist with extensive onboarding due diligence and ongoing monitoring experience across complex commercial clients. Chartered Financial&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<section>\n<p>Experienced compliance and risk manager with deep knowledge of global regulatory requirements and hands-on experience developing and implementing risk policies for a multinational publicly traded FinTech company.</p>\n<p>CAMS-certified AML/CTF specialist with extensive onboarding due diligence and ongoing monitoring experience across complex commercial clients.</p>\n<p>Chartered Financial Analyst with 14 years of expertise in research and valuation of multinational private and publicly traded companies across all credit risk profiles and sectors.</p>\n<p><strong>Languages:</strong> Native English and Russian</p>\n</section>\n<hr>\n<section class=\"experience\">\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-md.jpeg 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-lg.jpeg 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-xl.jpeg 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/fido_money_lending_ltd_logo-2xl.jpeg 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Risk Monitoring Manager</h3>\n<p><strong>Fido</strong><br>Jan 2025 – Present</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Fido’s platform and machine learning risk models make instant credit decisions for customers with no financial track record while reducing operational costs.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Assessed credit risk exposure across financial products and jurisdictions; identified emerging risks and implemented remediation strategies.</li>\n<li>Collaborated with data scientists to improve credit risk models using SQL and Python.</li>\n<li>Integrated risk insights into product design in partnership with tech and finance teams.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/Receive.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"151\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-xs.png 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-sm.png 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-md.png 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-lg.png 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-xl.png 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/Receive-2xl.png 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Head of Risk and Product</h3>\n<p><strong>Receive Corp.</strong><br>Jan 2024 – Jan 2025</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Receive is an Earned Revenue Access company for SMEs, backed by leading venture capital firms.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Built and led fraud and credit underwriting functions.</li>\n<li>Developed automated underwriting algorithms reducing manual processing time by 95%.</li>\n<li>Defined product strategy and launched daily cash flow forecasting tools.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/receive_recommendation-2.png\" data-size=\"567x567\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/receive_recommendation-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"567\" height=\"567\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/splitit-large.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"151\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-xs.jpg 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-sm.jpg 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-md.jpg 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/splitit-large-2xl.jpg 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Head of Underwriting and Policy</h3>\n<p><strong>Splitit Inc. (ASX:SPT)</strong><br>Jul 2020 – Dec 2023</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h4>Risk Management</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Credit risk underwriting and monitoring policy development.</li>\n<li>Development and maintenance of internal credit risk scorecards.</li>\n<li>Structuring B2B, B2C and B2B2C merchant deals.</li>\n<li>Ongoing fraud and transaction monitoring.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>AML / CTF Compliance</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>AML/CTF program development and internal audit.</li>\n<li>Onboarding due diligence policies and procedures.</li>\n<li>Monitoring funded merchants across North America and Europe.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_1.png\" data-size=\"655x378\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"378\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_2.png\" data-size=\"652x467\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"652\" height=\"467\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_3.png\" data-size=\"654x287\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_3-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"287\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_4.png\" data-size=\"656x350\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/splitit_recommendation_4-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"656\" height=\"350\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/CLA.png\" data-size=\"739x694\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/CLA-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"739\" height=\"694\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/CaringEye.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"139\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-xs.jpg 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-sm.jpg 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-md.jpg 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/CaringEye-2xl.jpg 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Product Manager &amp; Co-Founder</h3>\n<p><strong>Caring Eye Inc.</strong><br>Sep 2018 – Mar 2020</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Ranked among Israel’s Top 9 startups for parents by Calcalistech. Developed a smart video baby monitor using rPPG technology.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Conducted market research and user interviews.</li>\n<li>Defined product roadmap and prioritized features.</li>\n<li>Presented to investors and executive stakeholders.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/caringeye_recommendation.png\" data-size=\"655x556\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/caringeye_recommendation-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"556\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/RBC-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-xs.jpg 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-sm.jpg 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-md.jpg 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/RBC-small-2xl.jpg 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Commercial Credit Portfolio Manager – Mining</h3>\n<p><strong>Royal Bank of Canada</strong><br>May 2016 – Sep 2019</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Managed mining portfolio to prevent loan impairments.</li>\n<li>Structured complex credit facilities.</li>\n<li>Expanded key stakeholder relationships and exceeded targets.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/rbc_recommendation_1.png\" data-size=\"655x400\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/rbc_recommendation_1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"400\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/rbc_recommendation_2.png\" data-size=\"650x531\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/rbc_recommendation_2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"531\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"job\">\n<div class=\"job-header\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/HSBC-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"100\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-xs.jpg 300w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-sm.jpg 480w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-md.jpg 768w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/responsive/HSBC-small-2xl.jpg 1600w\"></figure>\n<div>\n<h3>Commercial Credit Portfolio Manager – Supply Chain</h3>\n<p><strong>HSBC Bank Canada</strong><br>June 2008 – May 2016</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Managed large credit portfolio across risk profiles.</li>\n<li>Recognized in HSBC global training materials for KYC/AML excellence.</li>\n<li>Proposed optimal financing solutions for acquisition and expansion plans.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/hsbc_recommendation_1.png\" data-size=\"656x525\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/hsbc_recommendation_1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"656\" height=\"525\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/hsbc_recommendation_2.png\" data-size=\"654x495\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://vakhromov-com.vercel.app/media/posts/3/gallery/hsbc_recommendation_2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"495\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</section>",
